data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: Military Robots: We pride ourselves on selling top of the line robots to aid in military procedures. Our legacy of collaboration with the US military has stayed strong since the 1960s and we have become a competitive arms dealer that you can trust! Whether it’s a robot that’s required for the thick of combat or minesweeper with a built in coffee maker, we have what you need.

data.name: TextBox2.Text
data.value: Household Robots: Kids keep making spills? Never know what to make for dinner? Too stressed from your job to ever clean? Perpetually exhausted? We have the solution for you! Our robots have been specially designed to aid in everyday tasks that are included but not limited to: Dishwashing, cooking, changing diapers, and even filling your taxes! Treat yourself to a break and see what we’re all about!

data.name: TextBox3.Text
data.value: Entertainment Robots: Come one come all! Our do it yourself robot allows the user to express themselves to the fullest! Recommended for all ages, our robot is simple enough for expanding a child’s budding mind but still has the capabilities of a complex machine that an adult can turn into a drone, clawbot, or RC car. Come see why we’ve been ranked as the hottest product on the market!
